Description=TPM-based key bootstrapping and system integrity measurement${Newline}Keylime is an open source scalable trust system harnessing TPM Technology.${Newline}${Newline}Keylime provides an end-to-end solution for bootstrapping hardware rooted${Newline}cryptographic trust for remote machines, the provisioning of encrypted${Newline}payloads and run-time system integrity monitoring. It also provides a${Newline}flexible framework for the remote attestation of any given `PCR` (Platform${Newline}Configuration Register). Users can create their own customized actions that${Newline}will trigger when a machine fails its attested measurements.
